* in GNS3 > edit > preferences > server > remote servers > add
*add the name, ip, port, user and password. all should be shown
in the gns3 VM ui. 

click ok > apply.


* preferences > GNS3 VM
click the box "Enable this GNS VM" 
chose "remote"
click apply and ok.



*in GNS vm, upgrade the VM to the latest version possible and reboot it, ands do the same
for GNS3 in windows.
